data.title: Prime Video: Last Action Hero
data.meta_description: Superstar Arnold Schwarzenegger breaks more than just the fourth wall in this adventure from acclaimed director John McTiernan where an eleven-year-old boy gets magically thrown into the world of his favorite action movie character.
data.text:
Last Action Hero

Superstar Arnold Schwarzenegger breaks more than just the fourth wall in this adventure from acclaimed director John McTiernan where an eleven-year-old boy gets magically thrown into the world of his favorite action movie character.
